name: HOTLIFE x MISFITS SILKSCREEN HALLOWEEN PRINT
description: We honored, and proud to say that the legendary horror punk band, The Misfits asked us to design their official Halloween 2013 Show Silkscreen Print. It is a one time, extremely limited edition piece of artwork, hand signed and numbered. Will be shipped in a poster tube.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "BACK IN BLACK" T
description: What makes the HOTLIFE "BACK IN BLACK" T so unique is the combination of ultra soft, low contrast, print techniques  with bold large artwork. The final product is smooth & comfortable in a low key, sophisticated style.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "OR DEATH" T
description: The all new HOTLIFE " OR DEATH" T is a high quality, heavyweight T with cistom printed inner tag, and sewn hangtag. Custom pocket print features oldschool HL grave line drawing, while back displayes the coffin artwork. Get into it.

name: ** HOTLIFE "2013 JINGLE BELLS HOLIDAY SWEATSHIRT" **
description:
The special HOTLIFE "2013 JINGLE BELLS HOLIDAY SWEATSHIRT" is a unique artistic concept, guaranteed to be the most beloved "ugly sweater" of the season. 

Perfect for a party, or family event. The trick to the perfect Holiday sweatshirt is the right mix of fun, and unusual. While everyone else is using a vulgar Xmas sweatshirt, or a predictable knit pattern design, HL stays ahead of the game with hand drawn, hand printed comic style art telling the classic tale of Jingle Bells, Batman Smells.... get into it.

Hand printed in FL on 50/50 Preshrunk, virtually pill free, garment with double-needle coverseaming on neck, armholes and waistband. 

Items ship USPS priority mail no later than Dec 12th.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "STILL DRE" T
description:
From the East Coast to the West Coast. Past, Present, and future, we always keep true to our roots...and we still got love for the streets. 

Highest quality. Hand made. LImited edition T.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "PATTERNS" Two Sided T
description: Front features hand printed, new style HL emblem while the back displays the triangle pattern filled with classic HL imagery. A over all mature, and laid back design, perfect for any season.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "SEEKERS" ZIP UP HOODIE
description:
Seekers of the truth.

Highest quality hand made hooded sweatshirt. Features custom sewn inner tag, inner pocket hold for headphones and hand printed graphics. HL hoodies have always been known for their excellent quality and we continue to raise the bar every year.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "STREETPUNK" T
description: The HL "STREETPUNK" T features ultra light weight, hand printed ink, for comfort, custom inner tag, and sewn hang tag. Artwork shows photo of NYC punk repping HOTLIFE.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "DESTROY" LONGSLEEVE
description: The "DESTROY" Long sleeve is a standard fit long sleeve, featuring original artwork, hand printed with ultra soft specialty inks, custom printed inner tag and sewn hang tag.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "SKELETON CREW" CREWNECK
description: The HL "Skeleton Crew" Crewneck Sweatshirt is top quality. Great fit. Hand made in FL. A comfortable fit, perfect alone, or layered for the Winter season.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "OLDSCHOOL" T
description:
The classics.

Hand made in FL. Best quality. Limited Edition. Get into it.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "MILEYSAURUS" T
description:
The only way to profess your love/hate for Miley, is to wear a shirt thats as crazy as she is. Limited Edition 100% Cotton Unisex T, hand drawn, and hand printed in sunny Florida, USA. Preorders ship between 9/30 and 10/5. 

Like riding a giant wrecking ball naked, you gotta get into it.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "UNLUCKY RED" Fitted Two Tone Patch Cap
description: Collectable and custom sewn patch fitted cap in bold red, with printed bill. Perfect match with the new HL "FTW" Red T

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "FTW" V.2
description: HOTLIFE - "FTW" T is a ultra soft ring spun cotton T with hand printed water based ink for ultra soft feel and comfort. The T also features hand sewn custom hang tag and printed inner tag. Ultra premium shirt, that will keep its shape and fit. Simple clean artwork, always in style.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "CUSTOM CAMO" 3/4 SLEEVE T
description: Highest quality3/4 sleeve features soft camo print sleeves and bold but soft printed illustration on the front, as well as custom inner tag. The baddest of the bad.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "KINGS OF THE COAST" CLASSIC SCRIPT
description: The classic black and white custom script "Kings of The Coast" style hand printed lightweight for summer. Custom hang HL hang tag and inner tag. We run it.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "MOLOTOV" T
description: A great representation of the HOTLIFE philosophy. Subculture, street movement, revolution. Where it is political, ethical, or any type of oppression, stand and fight and destroy what destroys you. The new HL "MOLOTOV" design. Hand printed two color front and back artwork, custom printed inner tag, all with specialty waterbased ink as well as sewn hangtag. Top quality as you would expect from the HL fam.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "KINGS OF THE COAST" Blend
description: The limited edition custom script "Kings of The Coast" style hand printed lightweight for summer but with a unique blend soft green inks for one of a kind look. Custom hang HL hang tag and inner tag. Collectable.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "UNSTOPPABLE" TIE DYE
description: One of the hottest and most classic looks for summer created to fit the darker HOTLIFE style. Darker color scheme with high contrast print of our "Unstoppable" seal design.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "BO TIME" T
description: The new "BO TIME" T features our beloved mascot BO wearing his favorite sunglasses. He is a rescued American bulldog with a great attitude and he maybe the worlds frisbee champion ha. The design is eyecatching, stylish, and the quality is unmatched. Features custom sewn hang tag and inner tag for comfort.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "Turquoise" Ladies Deep Vneck
description: With summer approaching, brighter colors, softer garments and ultra light printing are a must. This is a PREMIUM ladies deep Vneck with a very unique heather turquoise color and clean HOTLIFE athletic style logo hand printed with water based ink for maximum soft feel. Features custom printed inner tag and hand sewn hang tag. 100% Made in the USA

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "WOLFPACK" T
description: Ultra soft waterbased specialty printing, custom inner tag, custom sewn hang tag, top quality, perfect fit. 100% Made in the USA.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "SHARK BEACH" T
description: Shark beach is a more realistic spin on our belovedFLORIDA surf style. Features the beautiful contrast colors of charcoal and classic surf sea foam green. Hand printed with specialty soft inks, sewn hang tag and custom printed inner tag in the usual HOTLIFE fashion. This is why HL will for ever be the Kings of The Coast.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "DAGGER" Standard Tank Top
description: The new HOTLIFE - "DAGGER" Tank Top is available with the Fall Collection. A standard cut cotton tank with authentic sailor inspired hand illustrated linework. Features all the HL standards we all love like our custom printed inner tag, and sewn bottom hang tag. All made in Florida. and proud to be local. True American streetwear, ACTUALLY MADE IN AMERICA.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "FLAMINGO" CUSTOM POCKET T
description: Hand made in FL, very limited flamingo artwork on pocket. Custom printed inner tag and hang label. A must have for summer, and any collector.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - LADIES "CUSTOM CAMO" TANK TOP
description: HIgh quality, lightweight, racerback camo tank created specifically for ladies. A perfect release for summer.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "SUBCULTURE" TANK
description: High quality tank, hand printed with specialty soft waterbased ink, & featuring artwork from classic punk shows & music that helped to shape HOTLIFE into what it is today. HL has always been about expression, subculture, and DIY mentality and this really represents what we're about.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "DANNY BOY" T
description: One of our all time favorites. The new HL "DannyBoy" T speaks for itself. If you know who this is, you know this shirt is perfect for you. Features all the usual HOTLIFE specialties. Ultra soft, inner tag, hang tag, hand printed. Enjoy.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "HAVE MERCY" Ladies Tank
description: In an age where there is so much anger, hatred, and suffering, one must never forget to...Have Mercy. Two color water based eco friendly print features heart throb Uncle J playing his acoustic  (which he so wisely decorated with classic HL stickers) on a high end American Apparel Tank top. Unique, fun, and nostalgic..everyone will be instantly jealous.

name: *BRAND NEW*HOTLIFE - "SUMMER SHORTS" Ladies
description: HOTLIFE Limited Edition Girls shorts. Perfect for summer. High contrast  and high comfort. Features custom HL emblem hand printed on front corner, and HOTLIFE arched on back. Waterbased ink for ultra soft feel. Very cool, limited, & perfect for summer.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "HOOTLIFE"  Tank Top
description: Highest quality tank top featuring our classic HOOTLIFE artwork. Features custom sewn hang tag, and inner label, all hand printed in FL.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "UNLUCKY 13" Fitted Two Tone Patch Cap
description:
HOTLIFE "UNLUCKY 13" Fitted Two Tone Patch Cap. Printed and sewn in central Fl by the HOTLIFE Family. Unique pattern and the color scheme goes perfectly with almost every design in the Unlucky13 Collection. Available in two sizes:

SM/MD 

LRG/XL

Model Wearing LRG - XL

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "BLACK CAT" 3/4 Baseball T
description: Features illustrated Black Cat logo front and the new Unlucky Thirteen below. Custom printed inner tag. Ultra high quality. This is the softest T known to man. Pick one up.

name: HOTLIFE "UNLUCKY PUPPY" 3/4 Sleeve Dog Shirt
description:
There is nothing more rad then wearing the new "Unlucky13" 3/4 sleeve Shirt...and having your beloved pup matching. Ultra soft miniature matching 3/4 sleeve. Designer dog gear. Comes in S - XL.

Adult shirt sold separately. Duh.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "IT'S YOUR CHOICE!" T
description: A true streetwear T, the new HL "IT'S YOUR CHOICE" artwork is a tribute of a classic NY Lower East Side Crew style. Features the HOTLIFE Worldwide Crew pocket style print and back oldschool graffiti art. A must have for the streetwear collector, & NYHC enthusiast. DFTS.DFTS.

name: *SOLD OUT* HOTLIFE - "UNLUCKY13" TWO TONE & SEWN HOODIE
description: The new Unlucky13 Two Tone & Sewn hoodie is made environmentally sound with eco friendly materials and practices. Hand printed and sewn patches, made 100% in Florida. Features custom inner label, official Unlucky 13 Collection patch, premium drawstring ties, kangaroo front pocket and antiqued nickel zipper. Absolutely the most comfortable hooded zip available. All out comfort and style.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "NO REGRETS" PREMIUM TANK
description: Living life to the fullest. Living life with no regrets. Living the HOTLIFE 24/7. 100% Ring Spun Cotton premium Tank. Water based light weight specialty printing, unique two tone trim and cutom printed inner tag. Made in the USA...from California to the sunshine state.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "Retro Custom Pocket" T
description: Custom hand made high quality pocket T. Features red white and blue retro pattern. Sewn hang tag, & custom printed inner tag. Limited Edition.

name: *XL ONLY* HOTLIFE - "FAMILY" Zipup Hooded Longsleeve
description: The new HOTLIFE "Family" Zip Up Hooded Longsleeve is truly unique and awesome in so many ways. It features the standard HL custom printed inner tag, premium light weight, ring spun cotton, ...its almost TOO comfortable. Released with the Winter line, but a perfect pick all year round. Get one for yourself, or for your family & friends.

name: HOTLIFE - "HL EMBLEM" Air Fresheners
description: New car scent HL emblem air fresheners. Such a rad idea right? Take the Doritos locos wrappers outta your car, give it a good vacuum, and hang one of these bad boys from your rear view. Your car will look rad, it will be cooler, and it will smell fantastic.

name: *XS ONLY* HOTLIFE - "NEVER SAY DIE"
description: HOTLIFE - "NEVER SAY DIE" T, premium ring spun cotton XS T, with water based specialty print for absolute most soft feel possible. A fantastic bold design features classic working classic imagery. A must have for the streetwear enthusiast.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "NEVER SAY DIE V.2" T
description: Classic imagery for those who seek a life of adventure. This Goonies inspired artwork is printed with water based ink on ring spun cotton T for ultimate comfort. Be sure to pick one up and show your love for true cinematic genius.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "STREET KIDS"
description:
HOTLIFE "Street Kids" design released with the 2012 Fall Collection! 

Fun, stylish, super soft high quality threads, with the hottest hand illustrated artwork around. Matches with anything. Comfy, fresh and clean. If you like it, spread the word. HL killin it in 2012!

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "RAT PATROL"
description: The HOTLIFE "Rat Patrol" T. Hand illustrated artwork featuring the worlds most notorious rodent, cashin checks and breakin necks. Comes in the classic HOTLIFE style tradition with printed inner tag, hand sewn HL emblem hang tag on ultra soft ring spun cotton T. Made in Florida, USA!

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE x NEW ERA SNAPBACK HAT
description: The much anticipated official HOTLIFE x NEW ERA Snapback broidered, cut, sewn and assembled directly at the new Era factory. Features classic HOTLIFE script artwork on front, embroidered HL emblem on back, and Official New Era bill sticker and labe. The freshest look, the highest standard of cap. Grab one!

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "ALL THAT" T
description:
The HL "All That" T is a quality ring spun cotton T, hand printed with the worlds softest specialty printing for the most comfortable wear you can find. 

Whether you're chillin by the lockers with earboy and pizza face, or learning french in a bathtub, this shirt is all that. Get it.

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "AMERICAN DREAM"
description:
The HOTLIFE "American Dream" T. Features ultra soft water based, hand printed artwork, custom printed INNER tag, and sewn hang tag all made here in Florida. That means no heavy, uncomfortable prints. 

Super clean design, low key colors so it goes with anything and it just looks rad. Get one. 

www.livingthehotlife.com

name: HOTLIFE x A LOSS FOR WORDS Mashup Tank
description:
We're so fortunate to have such great friends, and we take a lot of pride in our HL crew and family. This is a limited edition collab tank top with A Loss For Words from Boston! You've seen them on tour constantly all over the world along side acts like The Wonder Years, Polar Bear Club, Transit, Cruel Hand, etc. 

The tank top features classic MA color scheme and jersey style print. Perfect for basketball, working out, stage diving, head walking, crowd surfing, or just looking like a bad ass. Will be available online exclusively here and at Warped Tour 2012 at the A LOSS FOR WORDS Merch Tent! Get it!

Check em out! http://www.facebook.com/aloss4words

name: *BRAND NEW* HOTLIFE - "CLASSIC BASEBALL" SNAPBACK
description:
*PERFECT MATCH WITH ANY OF THE NEW DESIGNS

This is a more classic style baseball fit Sitting just between a flat and traditional cap. Its the perfect mix for the classy look. One of three HL first edition snapback caps. This features the HOTLIFE embroidered white logo above gray laurel AND HOTLIFE trademark script embroidered on back right in flush white on a premium snapback. 

***All hats shipped separately in special boxes to maintain shape and quality.

name: *SOLD OUT* HOTLIFE - "HL ARMY" CUSTOM JACKET
description:
The HOTLIFE "HL ARMY" Custom Jacket!!! 

High end, high quality custom jacket. Features hand made, custom sewn inner size tag, custom hand sewn arm AND pocket patches. Muted army green blends a classic military look with the modern HOTLIFE styling. Wearable alone or with layers as pictured. A PERFECT limited edition fit for stayin warm in winter. Get it

name: "SOLD OUT* HOTLIFE - "BO" T
description:
The new HOTLIFE "BO" T is one of our most anticipated T's to date. Features beloved mascot, an amazing American Bulldog/Pitbull mix rescue who is a great representation of what HL is all about. A true underdog, strong, and level headed with true heart. The tee is quite literally the one of the softest most comfortable shirts you will ever own. Custom hand printed inner tag, sewn hang tag, and weightless water based hand printed graphic. Incredibly smooth and comfortable, and a fantastic conversation starter. 

Male model is wearing Med

description:
Everyone who knows HOTLIFE knows we set the standard when it comes to fresh, original hoodies. Our last "Rattlesnake" Hoodies sold out immediately and is rare and highly sought after, so be sure to grab this soon to be classic nyhc inspired/streetstyle hooded sweatshirt. High quality, soft hoodie. 

HL is worn by the elite and true loyal friends and family, thats why this will be kept limited edition just like last years. 

Weeeeeeee're The Crew!
